### Summary

Issue #343 removes the closed-set constraint on `type_hint`. The agent currently forces "Trip to Spain" into `type_hint: "task"` because only 6 entity types are recognized as non-surface types. The fix renames `_ENTITY_TYPES` → `_NONSURFACE_TYPES` (clarifying its sole purpose), updates prompt documentation to guide agents toward system types when they fit but allow custom lowercase nouns when they don't, and adds tests verifying the new behavior.

